    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant attention and investment from its next owner. The exterior shows heavy wear, including deep scratches, several large dents, and noticeable rust patches on the wheel arches and lower panels. Mechanically, the car requires a thorough inspection and likely major repairs to be roadworthy again, as it currently suffers from engine hesitation and a worn suspension. This is a project car suited for someone with the tools and time to restore it.",
